title: Ep. 251 - Even Socialists Don't Want To Live Under Socialism
description:
Today on the show, as socialist Venezuela falls apart before our eyes, it is disturbing to note that so many young people in America want that system in our country. Yet if socialism is a good system, why has it destroyed every country that tried it? Also, a Democratic state rep makes at once the most horrific but also must honest argument for abortion you’ll ever hear. Date: 05-02-2019
